  "Description": {
    "English": "A beautiful gemstone, this prized product is the engorged, luminescent berry of the <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Star Bramble</span>.<br><br>The host plant requires <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">lush conditions</span> to thrive in the wild, but can be farmed in all environments with the aid of a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Hydroponics Tray</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一颗美丽的宝石，它是<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">星辰灌木</span>珍贵又发光的果实。<br><br>宿主植物需要在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">繁茂条件</span>下才能在野外旺盛生长，但如果在<span class=\"name name-technology\">水培盘</span>中培养，则可以在任何环境生存。",
    "TencentChinese": "一颗美丽的宝石，它是<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">星辰灌木</span>珍贵又发光的果实。<br><br>宿主植物需要在<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">繁茂条件</span>下才能在野外旺盛生长，但如果在<span class=\"name name-technology\">水培盘</span>中培养，则可以在任何环境生存。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這種價格高昂的漂亮寶石，是<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">星刺灌木</span>飽滿發光的果實。<br><br>這種寄主植物需要<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">茂盛環境</span>才能在野外生長，但若借助<span class=\"name name-technology\">水耕盤</span>，便能在任何環境中栽種。"
  },
